WEBVTT

00:03:31.640 --> 00:03:36.936
They sent my older sister Claire and I
to our grandparent's,

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:39.880
hoping whatever was happening
would blow away.

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:45.680
Soon we had to escape from there, too.

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.816
We hid,

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.056
we crawled,

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:51.360
we sometimes ran.

00:03:56.840 --> 00:04:00.840
Sometimes I heard laughter